                <h5 class="fw-semibold">6. Responsibility  </h5>
                <p>The Customer is solely responsible for the contents of the invoice information transmitted to LHDN via EINV. The EINV system will perform checks on the information submitted to validate if the information has been filled in according to LHDN’s requirement prior to transmission to LHDN. 
