                    The Buyer could request for a rejection of the validated invoice, and Customer would cancel, on their own accord or on behalf of the Buyer, the validated Invoice within the 72 hours timeframe through EINV. 
                    If the cancellation requested is beyond 72 hours, the Validated Invoice could not be cancelled any more, and the Customer would have to create a Credit Note or Debit Note on EINV and the validation process with LHDN will be initiated</p>

