                <h5 class="fw-semibold">8. Subscription, Billing & Payment </h5>
                <p>
                    Customers are to subscribe to the annual subscription before they could use EINV for the submission of their Invoices. 
                    Payment needs to be received in full and in advance before the Customer can submit invoices on EINV. 
                    Subscription cannot be shared with another non-registered user. Subscription period will start on the 1st day of the month of when the payment is received. Once subscription begins, payment is not refundable and will continue until the end of the subscription period. 
                    Subscription will be auto-renewed for the following period, unless Datamation Technology is informed 3 months in advance for the cancellation of the subscription. The auto-renewal invoice will be sent to the Customer 3 months before the expiry of the current subscription period. 
                    Datamation Technology reserves the right to change the subscription prices from time to time. Any changes to the prices, subscription packages, and benefits will take place at the new subscription period and will not take effect on Customers with an existing subscription package. 
